<p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;This happened a few months ago:</p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We were on a road trip.</p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Suddenly, my dad pulled over at a McDonalds. We usually use their drive through, but this time my dad went inside.</p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;30-35 minutes later, he comes back. Wiping sweat off his forehead, he handed me a package saying 'here. That's a Happy Meal'.</p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Me: 'But we could have taken a carry out. In the drive through. And I'm not even hungry. Why did you go in and spend so much time there?'</p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;He: 'I had to check the Toy. Luckily, they had the one Minion you are missing in your collection.'</p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I'm 29!!</p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;This is just one example. I'm blessed with a father that is beyond cool! Both parents, actually :)</p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;"><br></p><p class="qtext_para" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 15px;"><a href="https://www.quora.com/What-is-it-like-to-have-a-cool-dad/answer/Manasi-Gadkari-1?srid=uLaia" target="_blank">Link</a></p>
